graph LR
    TrustyAI[TrustyAI Service Operator]

    %% External Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|cluster orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes 1.19+]
    TrustyAI -->|routes & OAuth| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.6+<br/>Optional]
    TrustyAI -->|ServiceMonitor CRD| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|watch & configure| KServe[KServe<br/>InferenceService CRDs]
    TrustyAI -->|environment injection| ModelMesh[Model Mesh]

    %% Integration Points
    OAuth[OpenShift OAuth Server] -->|authenticate users| TrustyAI
    Router[OpenShift Router] -->|external ingress| TrustyAI
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrape metrics| TrustyAI
    K8sAPI[Kubernetes API] -->|RBAC & resource mgmt| TrustyAI

    %% Service-level dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|stores data| PVC[PersistentVolumeClaim]
    KServe -->|inference data| TrustyAI
    ModelMesh -->|inference data| TrustyAI

    %% External services
    TrustyAI -->|service mesh| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>Not Required]

